{"tid":2135042,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"［突發］有手足大頭相被人貼左係黨鐵站入面！！！","createTime":"2020-08-01T07:01:24.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-02T05:45:33.000Z","uid":248120,"like":4,"dislike":13,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"996cff0a273c0478218ba0f1ec51382bce9ed9f1","tid":2135042,"uid":248120,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-01T07:01:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Ys1GxZJ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FYs1GxZJ.jpg&h=119d36e9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n大家係咪諗起one pun man入面<br />\n無牌騎士擲單車個段對白呢？<br />\n<br />\n<blockquote>》打唔贏你，我都要擋係你前面！》</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n如果你自認愛護手足<br />\n如果你一息尚存<br />\n不妨來旺角站北行月台朝聖下佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但記得一次唔好超過兩個人行埋<br />\n以免被綠魔抄牌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"xx-large\"><strong><span class=\"red\">轉風執位<br />\n手足歸位<br />\n一息尚存<br />\n抗爭到底<br />\n<br />\n香港人，八一建軍！</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong>⚠️免責聲明 Discreamer<br />\n一拳超人係中資手遊<br />\n一拳超人遊戲入面有政治審查<br />\n我唔係幫佢賣廣告<br />\n</strong>"},{"pid":"94765c32dcaac177643e673333a98c0e22806320","tid":2135042,"uid":213628,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-01T07:02:15.000Z","msg":"屌你隻手<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e6ea98efa6941c08212c0a2cffdc3cfb89778c2f","tid":2135042,"uid":165336,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-01T07:05:21.000Z","msg":"我去旺角都係搭巴士唔會搭黨鐵"},{"pid":"04